parent1.code: a picture of a golden phoenix rising in the style of art deco. It emerges from flames on a clock tower in the bustling metropolis on a sunset evening, spreading its wings, with geometric patterns and metallic accents adorning the cityscape.

parent2.code: a watercolor of a green dragon flying in the style of traditional Chinese painting. It soars through clouds on the misty peaks in the ancient mountains on a foggy morning, breathing fire, with pagodas and cherry blossoms dotting the landscape.

offspring.code: A sketch of three silver unicorns galloping in the style of surrealism. They leap on the iridescent plains in the dreamscape on a starry night, leaving trails of stardust, with floating crystals and melting clocks suspended in the ethereal atmosphere.
